g.text: Payer FSP requests quote from Payee FSP
Switch forwards quote request to Payee FSP
Payee FSP responds to quote request
Switch forwards quote response to Payer FSP
Switch returns error to Payee FSP
[Payee FSP calculation fails or rejects the request]
Payee FSP returns error to Switch
Switch returns error to Payer FSP
